n defused better earlier, before any open confrontation developed.  Although I still think Croatia willsurvive, it will lose a lot; but Bosnian Muslims may end up even worseoff.  However, their position now is so horrible that perhaps they do notsee it getting any worse.  The key point is: do they still have any hope left?If not, then all bets are off.Mr. Stojanovic is clearly very, very happy about this.  I'm deeply hurt.This is not about some "image" but about survival of a concept of apartnership which I believe is natural and essential for both Croatsand Muslims.  Sigh...Josip
